# source:   athena
# purpose:  Acknowledged vulnerability tracking -- records CVEs with no
#           available fix. Standard mode forces review when the set changes (fix
#           released or new no-fix CVE disclosed).
# baseline: Known unfixable CVEs. Changes here mean either a fix was released
#           (remove the line and patch) or a new unfixable CVE appeared (review
#           and accept).
# columns:  cve	package	version	fix_or_status
